subcategories.name: Axis
subcategories.description: Issues related to the axes of coordinated planes

subcategories.name: Legends and Scales
subcategories.description: Issues related to legends and the use of scales

subcategories.name: Color
subcategories.description: Issues in the use of colors

subcategories.name: Text
subcategories.description: Issues related to titles, annotations and labels

subcategories.name: Data
subcategories.description: Issues related to the underlying data, its sources and completeness

subcategories.name: Data Transformation
subcategories.description: Issues introduced when processing data or applying statistical transformations

subcategories.name: Graph Drawing
subcategories.description: Issues introduced in the graph drawing process, leads to missing graph elements or incomplete graph

subcategories.name: Perception
subcategories.description: Issues related to the weaknesses in human perception

subcategories.name: Message
subcategories.description: Visualizations that are trying to convey nonsense or illogical messages

subcategories.name: Coordinated
subcategories.description: Spatial meaning in x-, y-, or z-axes

groups.name: Grammar of Graphics
groups.description: Issues grouped by different components of a graph

groups.name: Visual Analytics Pipeline
groups.description: Issues grouped by different stages of visual analytics

tags.name: Selective Data
tags.description: Cherry-picking the scope of data, e.g., picking an arbitrary starting point of the time axis.

tags.name: Missing Values
tags.description: Null values in the chart that causes confusion.

tags.name: Redundant Values
tags.description: Items appear more than once in the chart.

tags.name: Questionable Data
tags.description: Dubious data source.

tags.name: Hypothetical Data
tags.description: Not real data, but drawn like backed by data.

tags.name: Arbitrary Binning
tags.description: Items are grouped arbitrarily.

tags.name: Items Out of Order
tags.description: Items are not sorted, or out of order.

tags.name: Percentage Not 100%
tags.description: Percentages do not add up to 100% in a whole-part relationship.

tags.name: Faulty Regression
tags.description: Improper use of statistics, e.g., a regression line with high error.

tags.name: Unreliable Forecasting
tags.description: Plotting future data points derived from unreliable prediction.

tags.name: Base Line Alignment
tags.description: Values are indexed or normalized by an unconventional method.

tags.name: Color Mismatch
tags.description: Mismatch between colors and the objects that they represent, e.g., blue for apples.

tags.name: Ineffective Color Scheme
tags.description: Ineffective color scheme, e.g., categorical colors for continuous variable.

tags.name: Disguised Visualization
tags.description: Looks like a visualization, but not visualizing any data, also known as non-sequitur.

tags.name: False Description
tags.description: Description and visualization do not add up.

tags.name: Improper Annotation
tags.description: Improper annotation or highlight.

tags.name: Invalid Connection
tags.description: Lines or arrows are connecting unrelated dots.

tags.name: Distorted Map Projection
tags.description: Distort map projection to encode information

tags.name: Absurd Scale
tags.description: Data is drawn to an unconventional scale.

tags.name: Incorrect Use of Log Scale
tags.description: Incorrect use of log scale.

tags.name: Dual Axes
tags.description: Plotting more than one different scale on a single dimension, most often the y-axis.

tags.name: Ineffective Encoding
tags.description: Chart is understandable, but unintuitive, there are better alternatives.

tags.name: Poor Positioning
tags.description: Poor positioning, alignment, or rotation of items.

tags.name: Plotting Error
tags.description: Valid encoding choice but incorrectly drawn, e.g., a glitch.

tags.name: Too Many Colors
tags.description: Too many colors, mostly related to the scalability issues.

tags.name: Misrepresentation
tags.description: The geometric shapes do not match the labelled values.

tags.name: Inconsistent Scale Across
tags.description: Different scales across related charts.

tags.name: Missing Item Labels
tags.description: Missing label for item details.

tags.name: Incorrect Item Labels
tags.description: Items are labeled with incorrect description.

tags.name: Missing Axis
tags.description: Axis is missing for a coordinated chart.

tags.name: Missing Axis Labels
tags.description: Axis is not labeled with tick marks.

tags.name: Incorrect Axis Labels
tags.description: Axis is incorrectly labeled.

tags.name: Inconsistent Tick Interval
tags.description: Intervals on an axis does not follow a scale.

tags.name: Inconsistent Time Interval
tags.description: Inconsistent time interval between data points.

tags.name: Missing Legend
tags.description: Legend is needed but missing.

tags.name: Flipped Axis
tags.description: Axis values are increasing in an unconventional direction.

tags.name: Truncated Axis
tags.description: Non-zero starting point on an axis that exaggerates or understates differences between items.

tags.name: Undistinguishable Colors
tags.description: Categorical colors are undistinguishable with each other.

tags.name: Unjustified Animation
tags.description: Eye beats memory, comparing changes across animation frames is impossible.

tags.name: Confusing Legend
tags.description: Lengend is not helpful in understanding the chart.

tags.name: Confusing Label
tags.description: Labels are hard to understand or not understandable at all.

tags.name: Cluttering
tags.description: Overwhelmed by visual clutter.

tags.name: Occlusion
tags.description: Some items are not visible in the visualization because of blockage by another item.

tags.name: Chart Junk
tags.description: Chart ornament that causes negative effect in understanding.

tags.name: Illegible Text
tags.description: Text in the chart are illegible.

tags.name: Visually Awful
tags.description: Very disturbing while looking at it.

tags.name: False Color Correlation
tags.description: Items with same or similar colors are not related.

tags.name: Unjustified 3D
tags.description: Unjustified use of 3D, it distorts the perceived size of the items.

tags.name: Area Encoding
tags.description: Incorrect use of area encoding that exaggerates or understates differences between items.

tags.name: Area Encoded Pictogram
tags.description: Pictogram is improperly scaled to reflect value differences.

tags.name: Not Understandable
tags.description: Cannot decode any data nor information.

tags.name: Faulty Whole Part
tags.description: Not whole-part relationship but draw as a chart for whole-part relationship like pie chart.

tags.name: Faulty Logic
tags.description: Conveying an illogical message.

tags.name: Missing Context
tags.description: Need background information in order to understand the message.

tags.name: Invalid Comparison
tags.description: Comparison between items that are incomparable.

tags.name: Just a Population Map
tags.description: The observed pattern is nothing more than the pattern of population density.

tags.name: Spurious Correlation
tags.description: Suggesting causal relationships from correlations.
